data.description: Come see this beautifully remodeled, turnkey 3 bedroom, 2 bath home, with 1 car garage on a large, fenced in corner lot with fruit trees. Light and bright with an open design connecting the kitchen and family room to the sunroom with panoramic views of the oversized yard. Room for pool. This home has a NEW ROOF, AC, and is fully protected with IMPACT WINDOWS AND DOORS. Whole house backup generator. This home in the Northshore neighborhood surrounding Lake Mangonia is an excellent investment and place to call home; located across from Lake Mangonia and is a few minutes from The Square, Dixie Hwy (Antique Row), Grandview, NORA District, Palm Beach Island, and PBI airport. Near Bak MSOA and Dreyfoos HS. Call for a private showing.
